general.desc: CIMC Vehicles (Group) Co Ltd is engaged in the manufacturing and sale of semi-trailers and truck bodies for specialty vehicles. The semi-trailers mainly include the following product lines, Container chassis trailers, Flatbed trailers & relevant derivative types, Curtain-side trailers, Van trailers, Refrigerated trailers, Tank trailers, and other special types of trailers. The truck body products include dump beds for dump trucks, mixers for mixer trucks, and a wide range of other truck bodies for specialty vehicles. Geographically, it operates in China, North America, Europe, and Other regions, out of which the majority is from China.
